{"title":"音符","authors":["张仁平"],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":4,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"音符"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张仁平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是音符，全国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十亿音符中的一个；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在长城牌的谱表上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中华激情地调配着我。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在战火中跳跃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去沙漠跋涉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞上星际浪漫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝着未来奔波。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任中华把我谱在哪里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我始终把美组合。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪怕只有半拍生命。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我也用瞬间的和谐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去完美中华的创作。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这雄伟的乐章里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一个短暂而永生的我……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是音符，中国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十亿音符中的一个。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我安当不响亮的无名，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也神往主音中的角色。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"音符中没有贵贱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有适合与不适合。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁能让乐章变得神奇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就应主动强化中华的魂魄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十亿灿烂的音符啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我们都无愧地说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是中华的灵感，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正被谱进壮丽的歌。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}